---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="제품 — 로직크래프트 LogicCraft"
  description="로직크래프트가 기획·디자인·출시까지 직접 만든 사고력 시리즈와 일상 도구들."
>
  <!-- ============ PAGE HERO ============ -->
  <section class="page-hero">
    <canvas class="hero-net" aria-hidden="true"></canvas>
    <div class="wrap">
      <p class="eyebrow on-dark">PRODUCTS · 전체 제품</p>
      <h1>우리가 만든 제품.</h1>
      <p class="lead">기획·디자인·출시까지 직접 만들었습니다. 사고력 시리즈와, 일상을 거드는 도구들.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============ SYNERGEION SERIES ============ -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="reveal">
        <p class="eyebrow">SYNERGEION 시리즈</p>
        <h2 class="section-title">3세부터 18세까지 이어 타는 사고력 라인업.</h2>
        <p class="section-lead"><a href="/synergeion" style="color:var(--blue);font-weight:700">시리즈 자세히 보기 →</a></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============ STUDIO PRODUCTS ============ -->
  <section class="products" style="padding-top:0">
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="reveal">
        <p class="eyebrow">STUDIO · 일상 제품</p>
      </div>

      <!-- 교육 -->
      <div class="section-block" style="margin-top: clamp(40px,5vw,64px)">
        <div class="cat-head reveal">
          <span class="label">교육</span>
          <span class="rule"></span>
          <span class="count">05</span>
        </div>
        <div class="card-grid">
          <article class="pcard reveal">
            <div class="top">
              <img class="icon" src="/icons/robotrail.png" alt="" />
              <div><div class="name-row"><h3>로보트레일</h3><span class="chip">컴퓨팅 사고력</span></div></div>
            </div>
            <p class="desc">코드 없이 명령 퍼즐로 코딩 사고력을 측정·훈련하는 앱. 학습 108판 + 측정 36문제 + 도전 모드.</p>
            <div class="links">
              <a href="https://apps.apple.com/kr/app/id6764465655">App Store</a>
              <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.smartsikhye.robotrail">Google Play</a>
              <div class="legal">
              <a class="muted" href="/apps/robotrail/support">지원</a>
              <a class="muted" href="/apps/robotrail/privacy">개인정보</a>
              <a class="muted" href="/apps/robotrail/terms">약관</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="pcard reveal">
            <div class="top">
              <img class="icon" src="/icons/science-club.png" alt="" />
              <div><div class="name-row"><h3>과학자 클럽</h3><span class="chip">과학</span></div></div>
            </div>
            <p class="desc">추측·발견·분기·회고 4단계로 매일 한 별씩 켜는 과학 사고 게임.</p>
            <div class="links">
              <a href="https://apps.apple.com/kr/app/id6771675434">App Store</a>
              <span class="soon-btn">Google Play (예정)</span>
              <div class="legal">
              <a class="muted" href="/apps/science-club/support">지원</a>
              <a class="muted" href="/apps/science-club/privacy">개인정보</a>
              <a class="muted" href="/apps/science-club/terms">약관</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="pcard reveal">
            <div class="top">
              <img class="icon" src="/icons/scienceapp.png" alt="" />
              <div><div class="name-row"><h3>왜 그렇게 생각해?</h3><span class="chip">융합 사고력</span></div></div>
            </div>
            <p class="desc">정답이 아니라 답에 도달하는 사고 과정을 9과목으로 훈련하는 자기주도 학습 플랫폼(웹).</p>
            <div class="links">
              <a href="https://logicschool.co.kr">바로가기 →</a>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="pcard reveal">
            <div class="top">
              <img class="icon" src="/icons/certnote.png" alt="" />
              <div><div class="name-row"><h3>모두의 자격증</h3><span class="chip">자격증</span></div></div>
            </div>
            <p class="desc">자격증 필기·실기 정리부터 기출 모의고사·실전 모드·암기카드·오답노트까지. 시험 공부를 한 곳에서.</p>
            <div class="links">
              <a href="https://apps.apple.com/kr/app/id6779944719">App Store</a>
              <span class="soon-btn">Google Play (예정)</span>
              <div class="legal">
              <a class="muted" href="/apps/certnote/support">지원</a>
              <a class="muted" href="/apps/certnote/privacy">개인정보</a>
              <a class="muted" href="/apps/certnote/terms">약관</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="pcard reveal">
            <div class="top">
              <img class="icon" src="/icons/topbattle.png" alt="" />
              <div><div class="name-row"><h3>브레인블레이드</h3><span class="chip">학습 배틀</span></div></div>
            </div>
            <p class="desc">팽이 배틀과 학습 퀴즈를 합친 두뇌 게임. 빠르고 정확하게 맞힐수록 강한 일격이 나가요. 구구단·영단어·한자·세계·바른말 5과목.</p>
            <div class="links">
              <a href="https://apps.apple.com/kr/app/id6780302277">App Store</a>
              <span class="soon-btn">Google Play (예정)</span>
              <div class="legal">
              <a class="muted" href="/apps/topbattle/support">지원</a>
              <a class="muted" href="/apps/topbattle/privacy">개인정보</a>
              <a class="muted" href="/apps/topbattle/terms">약관</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 일상 -->
      <div class="section-block">
        <div class="cat-head daily reveal">
          <span class="label">일상</span>
          <span class="rule"></span>
          <span class="count">03</span>
        </div>
        <div class="card-grid">
          <article class="pcard reveal">
            <div class="top">
              <img class="icon" src="/icons/ourfootprint.png" alt="" />
              <div><div class="name-row"><h3>커플맵로그</h3><span class="chip warm">지도</span></div></div>
            </div>
            <p class="desc">둘이 다녀온 동네가 색으로 칠해지는 커플 점령 지도. 우리만의 맛집 등급도 직접 만들어요.</p>
            <div class="links">
              <a href="https://apps.apple.com/kr/app/id6769797672">App Store</a>
              <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.logiccraft.ourfootprint">Google Play</a>
              <div class="legal">
              <a class="muted" href="/apps/ourfootprint/support">지원</a>
              <a class="muted" href="/apps/ourfootprint/privacy">개인정보</a>
              <a class="muted" href="/apps/ourfootprint/terms">약관</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="pcard reveal">
            <div class="top">
              <img class="icon" src="/icons/stockwatch.png" alt="" />
              <div><div class="name-row"><h3>불안한개미</h3><span class="chip warm">주식 시세</span></div></div>
            </div>
            <p class="desc">매매 없이 시세만 — 거치대·위젯·잠금화면으로 보는 한국 주식 시세.</p>
            <div class="links">
              <a href="https://apps.apple.com/kr/app/id6772662894">App Store</a>
              <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.logiccraft.stockwatch">Google Play</a>
              <div class="legal">
              <a class="muted" href="/apps/stockwatch/support">지원</a>
              <a class="muted" href="/apps/stockwatch/privacy">개인정보</a>
              <a class="muted" href="/apps/stockwatch/terms">약관</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="pcard reveal">
            <div class="top">
              <img class="icon" src="/icons/sedolal.png" alt="" />
              <div><div class="name-row"><h3>세상돌아가는거알아버리기</h3><span class="chip warm">시사·사회</span></div></div>
            </div>
            <p class="desc">정치 몰라도 OK. 친구처럼 알려주는 정치·시사 한 토막과 우리 동네 후보·의원 정리.</p>
            <div class="links">
              <a href="https://apps.apple.com/kr/app/id6770908480">App Store</a>
              <span class="soon-btn">Google Play (예정)</span>
              <div class="legal">
              <a class="muted" href="/apps/sedolal/support">지원</a>
              <a class="muted" href="/apps/sedolal/privacy">개인정보</a>
              <a class="muted" href="/apps/sedolal/terms">약관</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
